1. *Lep* dan je danas. (It's a beautiful day today.)
2. *Lepo* se osećam. (I feel good.)
3. *Lepe* žene su uvek privlačne. (Beautiful women are always attractive.)
4. Ona je *lepo* obučena. (She is nicely dressed.)
5. Mi smo *lepo* dočekani. (We were welcomed nicely.)
6. Oni su nas *lepo* pozdravili. (They greeted us nicely.)
7. Gosti su bili *lepi*. (The guests were nice.)
8. Ona je *lepa*. (She is beautiful.)